        "payload": "tree 6221dfd4b18441878f569704bac56e9342ea1f4c\nparent 1fa34f90a2ff19f62c3e2984baf66b400c66356c\nauthor nervana21 <205626986+nervana21@users.noreply.github.com> 1776388776 -0400\ncommitter nervana21 <205626986+nervana21@users.noreply.github.com> 1776449119 -0400\n\nrpc: Merge joinpsbts locktimes correctly\n\nA merged PSBT should use the maximum `nLockTime` amongst the PSBTs that\nhave at least one input with `nSequence` != `SEQUENCE_FINAL`. PSBTs\nwhose inputs are all `SEQUENCE_FINAL` do not constrain the locktime.\n\nDocument this in the help text and extend rpc_psbt tests.\n",
